<br>
Objects are summoned from the ether, that's the fifth element of which no mention is made in Everquest.  The ether is all around us and it's the medium through which light travels.<br>
<br>
Your second question is easy.  Pets don't turn against their master because they're under the spell of a semi-permanent charm.  Thus the pet becomes the magician's servant.  <br>
A pet can turn against his master if it's in turn charmed by another entity inimical to the mage.<br>
